dcterms:description: The MIMIC-III dataset contains a variety of patient data types, including discharge summaries, demographic details, interventions, laboratory results, physiologic measures, and medication information. It is used for ICD coding tasks and includes de-identified discharge summaries with annotated ICD-9 codes.
dcterms:title: MIMIC-III
